description:
As a merchant
  I can assign product to diff categories
name: Category and product assign

elements.name: Assign product to two diff categories

steps.name: I am on Admin Login Page
I fill correct account email to email field
I fill correct account password to password field
I click on login button
I should see successful login
I check intercom message notification frame and click clear intercom message button
I check intercom message notification frame and click intercom message close button
I check new feature alert notification frame and click new feature alert close button
I check and click exclude products panel close button
I check and click no thanks button
I am on Category Create Page
I fill "(dirty data) First Category" to category name field
I click on add button
I should be redirected to Category List Page
I click on 1st subcategory button of categories list
1st row of subcategories list should contain 'First Category'

embeddings.data: {"elementText":"(dirty data) First CategoryView products Edit Delete","expectText":"First Category"}

steps.name: I am on Category Create Page
I fill "(dirty data) Second Category" to category name field
I click on add button
I should be redirected to Category List Page
3rd row of categories list should contain "Second Category"

embeddings.data: {"elementText":"(dirty data) Second CategoryView products Edit Delete","expectText":"Second Category"}

steps.name: I am on Product Index Page
I input "Product for Checkout" to search field
I should be redirected to Product Index Page
I should see row of product checkbox
I click row of product checkbox for the same order of row of product name included "20th Product for Checkout"
I click row of product checkbox for the same order of row of product name included "19th Product for Checkout"
I select assign to categories of bulk actions dropdown
I click on 2nd categories checkbox
I click on assign button
I should see confirmation popover
I click on confirm bulk button
I should see alert
I am on Category List Page
I click view products button of categories list for the same order of row of categories list included "(dirty data) First Category"
I should be redirected to Category View Products Page
selected products should contain "19th Product for Checkout"

embeddings.data: {"elementText":"∞ 20th Product for Checkout1200000 NT$5 NT$1 19th Product for Checkout","expectText":"19th Product for Checkout"}
